scripts.comment: Transposing music refers to the process of moving the notes up or down by a constant interval (ie, changing the key). Given a list of notes, can you transpose them by the given number of steps? Edit the custom block on the left to get started!
A couple examples using the block are shown below!
The scripts below use the block to change the key then play a few different songs!
